com.android.gis

类 MapView

  • java.lang.Object
    • View
      • com.android.gis.MapView

  • public class MapView
extends View
    地图控件类
    地图控件类负责地图显示，实现用户、地图和数据的交互操作。

      • AttachWorkspace

        public void AttachWorkspace(Workspace workspace)
        将地图控件与工作空间建立关联
        参数:
        workspace - 工作空间对象
        备注:
        打开显示地图前需要调用此接口建立关联

      • Open

        public boolean Open(java.lang.String mapName)
        打开指定名称的地图
        参数:
        mapName - 地图名称
        返回:
        打开成功返回true，否则返回false
        示例代码:
          boolean bMapOpen = false;
          Workspace workspace = new Workspace();
          String strWKPath = "/sdcard/gis/world.sxwu";
          String strLicPath = "/sdcard/gis/";
          m_mapView =(MapView)findViewById(R.id.MapView);
          workspace.SetWorkPath("/sdcard/gis/");
          if(workspace.open(strWKPath){
              m_mapView.AttachWorkspace(m_workspace);
              int iMapCount = workspace.getMapCount();
              if(iMapCount>0){
                  String mapName = workspace.getMapNameAt(0);
                  bMapOpen = m_mapView.Open(mapName);
                  if(bMapOpen){
                      Toast.makeText(this, "打开地图成功!", Toast.LENGTH_LONG).show();
                      m_mapView.setUserAction(MapUserAction.PAN);
                  }else{
                      Toast.makeText(this, "打开地图失败!", Toast.LENGTH_LONG).show();
                  }
              }
          }

        public void SetCenter(Point2D pntCenter)
        设置地图中心点
        参数:
        pntCenter - 地图中心点坐标
        备注:
        坐标单位度或米
        示例代码:
          Point2D p2d = new Point2D();

          p2d.y = 40.057127;
          m_mapView.SetCenter(p2d);    //将（116.419655,40.057127）设置为地图中心点

                  Dataset dst = dataSource.GetDatasetAt(0);

      • AddThemeLayer

        public boolean AddThemeLayer(Dataset dataset,
                    Theme theme)
        将专题图添加到当前地图中显示
        参数:
        dataset - 数据集对象
        theme - 专题图
        返回:
        添加成功返回true，否则返回false
        示例代码:
          Layer layer = m_mapView.GetLayer("BaseR@Jingjin");
          Dataset dst = layer.GetDataset();
          ThemeLabel themeLabel = new ThemeLabel();
          themeLabel.setExpression("NAME");
          TextStyle textStyle = new TextStyle();
          textStyle.Align = TextStyle.Align_Center;
          textStyle.ForeColor = Color.RED;
          textStyle.Weight = 20;
          textStyle.IsBold = true;
          themeLabel.setLabelStyle(textStyle);
          if (themeLabel.isValid()) {
              m_mapView.AddThemeLayer(dst, themeLabel);
          }
          m_mapView.Refresh();

      • SetPrjCoordSys

        public boolean SetPrjCoordSys(PrjCoordSys prjCoordSys)
        设置地图坐标系统
        参数:
        prjCoordSys - 坐标系统信息
        返回:
        设置成功返回true,否则返回false
        示例代码:
          PrjCoordSys prjCoord = new PrjCoordSys();
          GeoCoordSys geoCoord = new GeoCoordSys();
          PrjParams prjParm = new PrjParams();
          prjCoord.SetTypeID(PrjCoordSys.PCS_USER_DEFINED);
          prjCoord.SetProjection(PrjCoordSys.PT_GAUSS_KRUGER);
          geoCoord.dAxis = 6378245.0;
          geoCoord.dFlatten = 0.00335232986925914;
          geoCoord.dPrimeMeridian = 0.0;
          prjCoord.SetGeoCoordSys(geoCoord);
          prjParm.dFalseEasting = 500000.000000;
          prjParm.dFalseNorthing = 0.000000;
          prjParm.dCentralMeridian = 123.000000;
          prjParm.dStandardParallel1 = 0.000000;
          prjParm.dStandardParallel2 = 0.000000;
          prjParm.dScaleFactor = 1.000000;
          prjParm.dCentralParallel = 0.000000;
          prjParm.dAzimuth = 0.000000;
          prjParm.dFirstPointLongitude = 0.000000;
          prjParm.dSecondPointLongitude = 0.000000;
          prjCoord.SetPrjParams(prjParm);
          boolean bRt = m_mapView.SetPrjCoordSys(prjCoord);
